		<div class="comment" id="comment-6204">
	<p><cite>Comment by <a href='http://www.dkworldwide.com/techlife' rel='external nofollow'>Dave Kaufman</a> &#8212; May 05 2006 @ <a href="#comment-6204">7:35 am</a></cite> </p>

			
	<p>14.  Put it in writing.  This is smart on 2 fronts.  First it is impressive to get a <acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym> that is nicely formatted and has a cover letter, work arrangements, terms and conditions and a signature section.</p>
<p>Second it helps everyone understand exactly what will and won&#8217;t be done.</p>
<p>Work smart.</p>
