<p>I&#8217;m not necessarily talking about paying clients here - there are loads of projects that people take on regularly that they are doing for low to no cost where they eventually lose the passion. Like I said - if you&#8217;re doing too much work for free, and don&#8217;t have a great passion for it, get away.</p>
