	<p>Thank you, Derek. Although Romania hasn&#8217;t been introduced to fax spam, I&#8217;d still say don&#8217;t buy a fax machine at all. There is electronic fax, and that you can control from your PC or mobile. And by all means, do rise prices every year.</p>
