	<p>Nice advice Derek!  I can see that you have a quality that is needed in small business owners - a sense of humor.  I&#8217;ll be watching your site.  In my consulting practice, I have seen too many small businesses die an early death because they were so deep in the trees that they did not see the woods.  You need to know what you&#8217;re good at and then deliver excellence in what you do every time - sounds like you get that.  Keep it up.</p>
