<!--h2><img src="/images/aboutdf.jpg" alt="About Derek Featherstone" /></h2>
<p style="margin-top: 0;">Derek Featherstone is a former high school teacher turned <a href="http://www.furtherahead.com">web developer</a>, speaker, technical trainer, <a href="http://www.furtherahead.com/accessibility/">accessibility consultant</a>, and a long-time believer in web standards.</p-->

<h4>Working</h4>

<p>My web development and accessibility consultancy is <a href="http://furtherahead.com">FurtherAhead</a>, based in Ottawa, Canada, with clients around the world. And I'm not just saying that.</p>


<!--p style="margin: 1em 0;" ><a href="http://north08.webdirections.org"><img src="/images/wdn-speaker-350x120.gif" alt="Hear me speak at Web Directions North, January 28 - Feb 2, 2008" /></a></p-->



